    <div class="faq-a" id="how-much-should-i-charge-for-agency-services-per-m"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>The standard range for small-to-mid-size business services is $1,500–$5,000 per month. Local SEO for a single-location business typically falls between $1,500 and $2,500. National campaigns start at $3,000–$5,000 and scale from there. Use the base hourly cost formula to establish your floor, then price above it based on the value you deliver.</p></div></div>
