    <div class="faq-a" id="what-should-i-include-in-a-monthly-retainer"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>At minimum: technical monitoring, content production (blog posts or landing pages), on-page optimization for existing pages, and monthly reporting. Higher tiers add link building, competitor analysis, digital PR, and quarterly strategy sessions. Define deliverables precisely in the contract. Vague retainers create scope disputes.</p></div></div>
