    <div class="faq-a" id="how-do-i-price-services-for-small-businesses"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Start by understanding what small businesses are comparing your proposal against. Most small businesses have budgets of $500–$2,500 per month. If your cost floor is above $1,500, target small businesses where the scope actually fits that range. Not ones who want full-service work at $500.</p></div></div>
